fields.title: XPDS18
fields.description: HiDow’s latest and most advanced model of wired devices for muscle recovery and pain relief, the XPDS 18. Take your EMS experience to the next level with 6 new modes and functions.

fields.title: XPD12
fields.description: The new and improved XPD12 is a powerhouse when it comes to value. 6 pain relief (TENS) and 6 muscle enhancement (EMS) functions make it one of the most popular units in the HiDow lineup.

fields.title: XP
fields.description: The Acu XP micro is perfect for those who are serious about relief, but beginners with the technology. It offers the main therapies and just a few extras and still has a dual output for larger or multiple treatment areas.

fields.title: Wireless
fields.description:
Introducing HiDow’s newest multi-stim model, the Pro Touch Wireless 6-12 is a premium electronic muscle stimulator without the hassle of wires.

Now you can experience Transcutaneous Electrical Nerve Stimulation (TENS) and Electrical Muscle Stimulation (EMS) on the go, during any exercise or workout, all in the comfort of your own space while wearing any clothing comfortably overtop.

fields.title: Acubelt
fields.description: The belt-style cutaneous garment electrodes are intended to be used with all HiDow electrical stimulating devices. The package includes 2 straps of different lengths that allow you to place the belt-style garment electrodes on various areas. It may be used on the lower back area with the longer strap and legs and arms using the shorter strap.

fields.title: Acuknee
fields.description:
The knee style cutaneous garment electrodes are intended to be used with all HiDow electrical stimulating devices.

The knee style cutaneous garment electrodes will deliver the stimulation signals generated by the stimulator to the body surface with which they are in contact. The garment electrodes are made up of conductive silicone rubber.

fields.title: Acusocks
fields.description:
The HiDow Sock style accessories are cutaneous electrodes intended to be used with HiDow TENS/EMS stimulating devices.

The Sock accessory electrodes are non-sterile reusable OTC conductive garments intended to deliver the stimulation signals generated by the stimulator to the feet.

Adult use only.

fields.title: Acugloves
fields.description:
The HiDow Glove style accessories are cutaneous electrodes intended to be used with HiDow TENS/EMS stimulating devices.

The glove accessory electrodes are non-sterile reusable OTC conductive garments that are intended to deliver the stimulation signals generated by the stimulator to the hands.

fields.title: Acushoulder
fields.description:
The shoulder style cutaneous garment electrodes are intended to be used with all HiDow electrical stimulating devices.
The shoulder style cutaneous garment electrodes will deliver the stimulation signals generated by the stimulator to the body surface with which they are in contact.
